Class DayofYearSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • dayofyearsetpackage.DayofYearSet
  • public class DayofYearSet
extends java.lang.Object

    DAYS OF THE YEAR!

    Each DayofYearSet objects has DayofYear array inside it. DayofYear is inner class that has day and month value.
